    "content": "<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">为了帮助您快速了解微上客全渠道客服系统，以及可以在您的手机</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333;background:white\">APP</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">上集成的功能，我们为您准备了一个</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333;background:white\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">商城</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333;background:white\">”Demo</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">。您可以先使用</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333;background:white\">“</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">商城</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333;background:white\">”Demo</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">进行体验。</span></p><h2><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步：注册微上客客服账号</span></strong><br></h2><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:宋体\"></span></strong></p><hr><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">在微上客试用注册页面，填写账号密码及您企业域名等信息，注册微上客试用账号</span><br></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:14px\">官网注册的账号默认为管理员账号，登陆后可创建客服账号及变更添加角色</span></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-1-1-1.png\"></p><h2 style=\"white-space:normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步：绑定微信公众号</span></strong></h2><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:宋体\"></span></strong></p><hr><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">1、</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-stretch:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体\">登陆微上客，进入“管理员模式”</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体\">渠道管理</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体\">添加消息渠道</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体\">点击微信</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">logo</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体\">，添加微信公众账号</span><br></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:宋体\"></span></strong><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-1-1-2.png\"></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333;background:white\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">、点击</span><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333;background:white\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">点击进入扫码</span><span style=\"font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#333;background:white\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\">，进入微信公众平台，扫描二维码授权微上客平台。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;color:#333;background:white\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-1-1-3.png\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">3<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">、扫码授权即可</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-1-1-4.png\"></p><h2 style=\"white-space:normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">第</span></strong><strong>3</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">步：下载</span></strong><strong>APP</strong><strong><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">登陆</span></strong></h2><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24px;font-family:宋体\"></span></strong></p><hr><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"></span></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">1、</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-variant-numeric:normal;font-stretch:normal;line-height:normal;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体\">微上客全渠道不仅提供</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">web</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体\">网页版，还提供</span><span style=\"font-size:14px\">APP</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体\">移动版。</span><br></p><p style=\"white-space:normal;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\">请扫码下载微上客</span>APP<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">，也可以在</span>App Store<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">中搜索</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体\">“微上客”下载</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space:normal;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-1-1-5.png\"><br>2、打开app输入客服账号登陆、密码、及企业域名。在线处理各渠道客户消息</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space:normal;text-indent:28px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-1-1-6.jpg\"> <img src=\"assets/mock/img/a-1-1-7.jpg\"></span></span></p><p style=\"white-space:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"></span><br></p><p><span style=\"font-family:宋体\"><br></span></p><p><br></p>"
